273
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] prihvatili i moli Boga da se u tom proslavi.

274
00:28:20,079 --> 00:28:23,660
[SPEAKER_00] Zanimljivo je, ne mogu sad u detalje, jer se neke stvari snimaju,

275
00:28:23,660 --> 00:28:28,880
