288
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:29,640
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo vrlo brzo, hvala Bogu, opet uspjeli ostati trudni,

289
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] zahvaljujući toj metodi.

290
00:29:31,180 --> 00:29:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, i treća beba je ponovo, ponovo otišla.

291
00:29:37,640 --> 00:29:41,519
