299
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] i molim te, očisti nas od svega onoga što nas odaljava od tebe

300
00:30:13,599 --> 00:30:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] i od svega onoga što nas ne približava tebi.

301
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:20,079
[SPEAKER_00] Paldite, to može biti sve, to može biti noge,

302
00:30:20,079 --> 00:30:25,279
