303
00:30:25,279 --> 00:30:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali smo tako molili.

304
00:30:26,619 --> 00:30:29,660
[SPEAKER_00] A znate, kad gospodina molite da vas očisti,

305
00:30:29,660 --> 00:30:34,099
