307
00:30:37,779 --> 00:30:40,579
[SPEAKER_00] I to je često bolno, ali mislim da je to potrebno.

308
00:30:40,579 --> 00:30:43,960
[SPEAKER_00] I kogod je bilo teško, drago mi da smo to molili,

309
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:46,200
