318
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:13,099
[SPEAKER_00] Prometa je bilo i dobiti svega,

319
00:31:13,099 --> 00:31:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali nikad ne bi imali novaca i svako ljeto bi bio totalno bez novaca.

320
00:31:16,119 --> 00:31:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] I onda smo odlučili samo kucat račune

321
